task.summary: Change algorithms of AI, but not working correctly yet
AI update tested, critical errors not found. Some important bugfixes
Added encounter system without UI elements
Added floating text messages for damage and other info about attacks
Skill target displaying, only one skill at turn and death trigger.
Happy birthday! One year of work. And... Core of this project is ready (almost)
Reworked system of Plays and target choosing for skill's actions. And now dungeon randomly generates room types.
Reworked system of Plays and target choosing for skill's actions. And now dungeon randomly generates room types.

Fixed bug with double room opening when you tries to get through other then opener doors. You no longer can activate skill in movement. Skills rebalanced to get ability to win this game. But new balanced is not tested enough. Package name changed. (this is not final version of package name)
You no longer need (can) set params of Effect in constructor. Now you have abstract getter methods which will be used to describe everything about effect
Bug fixed. Now floor effects can be deleted for real.
